Namespace
osu.Framework.Allocation

A DependencyContainer which caches a TModel and members it contains attached with a CachedAttribute as dependencies.

public class CachedModelDependencyContainer<TModel> : IReadOnlyDependencyContainer where TModel : class, IDependencyInjectionCandidate, new()

Type Parameters

TModel

The type of the model to cache. Must contain only Bindable<T> fields or auto-properties.

Remarks

Users can query the model by directly querying for the TModel type, and query for the model's dependencies by providing the TModel type as a parent.
